						               													<description>From the quick paced, deep decision rich, abstract strategy BattlessonTM game, Battle of 4 Armies, it's expansion kit has finally been brought to the fantastical battlefield. In the Battle of 4 Armies expansion kit: The Battle is Joined, a new Falcon Army spreads its wings and adds another element to the game. Each Hero (including the new army of flying units) now has a set of abilities that are both bold and cunning, giving you that extra chance to be victorious.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How will you sieze the Riverport of Chip? Find out with the Battle of 4 Armies expansion kit: The Battle is Joined!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Note, the Battle of 4 Armies Expansion Kit is not a &amp;lsquo;stand alone&amp;rsquo; game. You must own a copy of Battle of 4 Armies to use this expansion kit.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Data:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Complexity: 1.5 on a 9 scale&amp;#10;Solitaire Suitability: 8.5 on a 9 scale&amp;#10;Scale: Each unit represents a single troop of fantasy warriors.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Components:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    One 1-page, color instructions sheet&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    5 Hero cards&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    10 color, die-cut 1&amp;rdquo; mounted game pieces&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
